  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">As we continue to develop our business, we might sell or buy additional services or business units. In such transactions, user information generally is transferred along with the rest of the service or business unit. Also, in the event that IMDb, Inc., or substantially all of its assets are acquired, user information will of course be included in the transaction.</evidence>
