  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">In compliance with the US-EU and US-Swiss Safe Harbor Principles we endeavor to resolve all complaints about privacy and the collection or use of customer information If you have questions about our participation in the Safe Harbor program or have a complaint please send an e-mail to safeharbor amazon com</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

